{"tid":2189550,"cid":5,"subCid":10,"title":"全民檢測 國產保護衣非醫療用  採樣醫護斥離譜","createTime":"2020-09-05T03:35:42.000Z","updateTime":"2020-09-05T05:21:15.000Z","uid":25558,"like":9,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":14,"replies":[{"pid":"f7b049df712b720a10f82ed03d4fa3c35224c279","tid":2189550,"uid":25558,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-09-05T03:35:42.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://hk.appledaily.com/local/20200905/EWWPZMYFD5GAVP5K2M25VFF5WQ/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.appledaily.com%2Flocal%2F20200905%2FEWWPZMYFD5GAVP5K2M25VFF5WQ%2F&d=RlZLtXxvTyjhSejQ4AJs4%2Bbr9%2BGymSeLOXabm6KdyvY%3D&h=2d79cd6a\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.appledaily.com%2Flocal%2F20200905%2FEWWPZMYFD5GAVP5K2M25VFF5WQ%2F&h=33788245\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://hk.appledaily.com/local/20200905/EWWPZMYFD5GAVP5K2M25VFF5WQ/</a><br />\n<br />\n節錄<br />\n<br />\n全民檢測 國產保護衣非醫療用 <br />\n採樣醫護斥離譜<br />\n<br />\n【本報訊】中國式病毒檢測由中央政府支配採樣方式，無法定資格內地人員負責化驗，連檢測中心人員的保護衣也是made in China。政府宣佈延長普及社區檢測計劃四日，卻未能向檢測人員提供合格裝備。有在檢測中心負責採樣的醫護人員揭發政府向他們提供「非醫用」防塵衣作保護袍，批評做法離譜；醫護工會憂慮增加播毒風險，「如果係非醫用，保護唔到醫護。」<br />\n<br />\n相關新聞：結果公佈遲 作用成疑<br />\n<br />\n記者：陳沛冰 張文鈴<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://hk.appledaily.com/resizer/3gEMNXcmsHG2KQ4FF6_ggYt13x4=/1029x1463/filters:quality(100)/cloudfront-ap-northeast-1.images.arcpublishing.com/appledaily/KQFCS74365EPXGSQKOP543PUNE.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.appledaily.com%2Fresizer%2F3gEMNXcmsHG2KQ4FF6_ggYt13x4%3D%2F1029x1463%2Ffilters%3Aquality%28100%29%2Fcloudfront-ap-northeast-1.images.arcpublishing.com%2Fappledaily%2FKQFCS74365EPXGSQKOP543PUNE.png&h=175ca1f4&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n■採樣人員保護衣上的標籤以英文及簡體字列明「Non Medical Use」及「非醫療用」。讀者提供圖片<br />\n<br />\n普及社區檢測計劃自9月1日至昨晚8時，。。。。<br />\n<br />\n相關新聞：有病徵者往檢驗 醫生憂播毒<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://hk.appledaily.com/resizer/1wGzL8I41k4s6KCFVSQ6FuQEBdo=/2424x1733/filters:quality(100)/cloudfront-ap-northeast-1.images.arcpublishing.com/appledaily/4TVUJ2MJLRAH5CUTEBAIFKKVRI.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.appledaily.com%2Fresizer%2F1wGzL8I41k4s6KCFVSQ6FuQEBdo%3D%2F2424x1733%2Ffilters%3Aquality%28100%29%2Fcloudfront-ap-northeast-1.images.arcpublishing.com%2Fappledaily%2F4TVUJ2MJLRAH5CUTEBAIFKKVRI.jpg&h=ceab6eab&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n■在檢測中心負責採樣的醫護人員均會穿上由政府提供的保護衣。 資料圖片<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://hk.appledaily.com/resizer/0AwT_GzPH9MoG-uD5YG3VYRxBbQ=/774x716/filters:quality(100)/cloudfront-ap-northeast-1.images.arcpublishing.com/appledaily/FIMA5TZSVRE3LATMK5IYDQ3IDQ.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.appledaily.com%2Fresizer%2F0AwT_GzPH9MoG-uD5YG3VYRxBbQ%3D%2F774x716%2Ffilters%3Aquality%28100%29%2Fcloudfront-ap-northeast-1.images.arcpublishing.com%2Fappledaily%2FFIMA5TZSVRE3LATMK5IYDQ3IDQ.jpg&h=16ceed72&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n■保護衣的包裝有用簡體字寫明非醫用，標示由「東莞市東方鴻業製衣廠」生產。<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n計劃延長四日 19中心停用<br />\n<br />\n公務員事務局長聶。。。。<br />\n<br />\n假大空的檢測計劃卻沒有安全裝備作後盾。有灣仔會議展覽中心負責採樣的醫護人員向本報提供相片，顯示保護衣的包裝有一張用簡體字寫的「合格證」，標示該即棄防塵衣由「東莞市東方鴻業製衣廠」生產，合格證上列明是「非醫用」。另一相片顯示，保護衣上的標籤同樣以英文及簡體字列明「Non Medical Use」及「非醫療用」。<br />\n<br />\n該名醫護人員批評，。。。。<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n僅每次更換手套感染風險大<br />\n<br />\n醫管局員工陣線主席余慧明指出，據醫管局內部指引，醫護人員接觸懷疑武漢肺炎患者時需穿一級保護衣，「如果係非醫用，即係一級都冇，保護唔到醫護」。醫護人員在醫院採樣會在負壓病房進行，且每次會更換保護衣，但檢測中心採樣人員僅每次更換手套，「𠵱家檢測中心的確出現確診者，如果唔係着醫用保護衣，可能將病毒傳畀下一個檢測嘅人，大家想像吓風險有幾大？」<br />\n<br />\n為免參與普及社區檢測計劃人數太少難看，政府容許市民檢完又檢。聶德權辯稱：「有市民可能去完高風險地區或接觸過高風險人群，覺得唔安心，再預約檢測都係理解。」<br />\n<br />\n政府發言人回應稱，政府。。。。。"},{"pid":"c8a70ebcd17fc2357c9baa6a365d9844134d4361","tid":2189550,"uid":41974,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-09-05T03:36:55.000Z","msg":"唔杯葛呢單嘢？"},{"pid":"94540dfe80e25d6feda7a9e2c806f1de47bb2186","tid":2189550,"uid":58630,"like":6,"dislike":0,"score":6,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-09-05T03:37:57.000Z","msg":"戲服黎<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"6a32993d6f2b255dd71d43e04262adfbda1aa989","tid